Privacy policy
Effective Date: April 24, 2023


Introduction:
This is a Kannada Kali app developed by User sencial App Development. This is a reading assistant app intended to help grade 4,5,6 students especially. This is not a school substitute. This is very rigidly aligned to karnataka state text books. This is after school reading practice. This all provides curated kannada to english translations which aim at improving kannada comprehension of english medium students. And word level english meaning aimed at helping granular comprehension. There is also a curated list of difficult words and sounds to help practice any specific difficulty a student may be facing pronouncing an alphabet or word.

Information We Collect
Personal Information You Provide:
We may collect Parents/Caregivers phone number and email in website or in person video call at the time of introduction or onboarding call. 

Information Collected automatically In the app:
App collects lines, words read, and alphabets pronounced correctly.
App collects screens and user interaction ‘usage data’.

Data Collection Methods:
Usage data is collected automatically through the app. Reading progress data is collected on user reading sessions completed.

App collects lines, words read, alphabets pronounced correctly to show reading progress and in future build ability to create personalized learning tasks.
App collects screens and user interaction ‘usage data’ to understand which features are not having good engagement which intern would help analyze and improve user experience.
App does not ask students to input any personal information.

Third-Party Services:

App collects data of reading progress and stores it in Google Firebase Firestore. Usage Data is collected using google firebase analytics call and store in google firebase analytics. The app does not show ads of any sort.
